<h2>Which AI SDR Tool Is Right for You?</h2>
<p>The right choice depends on your team size, budget, motion, and tolerance for AI autonomy. Below is the decision framework we use with our own customers.</p>
<p><strong>By budget:</strong>
- <strong>Under $200/month:</strong> Apollo (free tier) or Smartlead/Instantly for cold email
- <strong>$200 to $1,000/month:</strong> Reply.io, Regie.ai Pro, or Apollo paid
- <strong>$1,000 to $3,000/month:</strong> AiSDR or Artisan for autonomous
- <strong>$3,000+/month:</strong> AiSDR Scale, Outreach, or 11x for enterprise</p>
<p><strong>By team size:</strong>
- <strong>Solo founder:</strong> Apollo free + Clay free + Smartlead
- <strong>Small team (2-5):</strong> AiSDR or Apollo Professional
- <strong>Mid-market (5-20):</strong> Reply.io, Apollo Organization, or AiSDR Growth
- <strong>Enterprise (20+):</strong> Outreach with Clay underneath, or 11x for autonomous</p>
<p><strong>By motion:</strong>
- <strong>Cold outbound:</strong> AiSDR or 11x for autonomous; Smartlead for DIY
- <strong>Account-based:</strong> Lemlist for personalization, Outreach for orchestration
- <strong>Inbound-led:</strong> Common Room plus Apollo for follow-up
- <strong>PLG plus sales:</strong> Common Room plus AiSDR for product-qualified outreach</p>
